# ─── Local spike corpus — NEVER committed ────────────────────────────────────
# test/ holds third-party music (~651 MB) used only for local spike work:
#   test/test_playlist/     104 CC-BY / CC0 tracks (Free Music Archive)
#   test/other_extension/   format samples for the docs/02 §4 allow-list checks
# It is the corpus for docs/15 S3 (metadata) and S4 (crossfade). Committing it
# would also contradict legal/THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES.md ("TickTune ships no
# third-party audio").
#
# NOTE the leading slash: /test/ (corpus, ignored) is one character away from
# tests/ (the committed suite dir required by docs/13 §3). Never drop it.
/test/

# Committed E2E fixtures are self-made ~5 s tones (docs/13 §3) — keep them
# reachable even if a broad audio-extension rule is ever added below.
!/tests/e2e/fixtures/

# ─── Dependencies & build output ─────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
dist/
.astro/
.wrangler/
.output/

# ─── Test & coverage artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────────────
coverage/
test-results/
playwright-report/
blob-report/
.playwright/

# ─── Environment & secrets ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.local

# ─── Editors, agents & OS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
# Claude Code worktree checkouts live here — full working copies, never tracked.
.claude/worktrees/
*.swp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ─── Logs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
npm-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
